{"type": "article", "id": 3789, "title": "Italesse 香槟酒杯", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-24T08:18:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233306vK3Pix40JUFhrQd9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利葡萄酒专业杯具品牌 Italesse 日前邀请斯德哥尔摩的设计工作室 Claesson Koivisto Rune，为其设计了一款名为「Richard Juhlin Optimum」的香槟酒杯。擅长品酒的人对酒具素来有着苛刻的要求，而 Claesson Koivisto Rune 团队显然是懂酒之人，他们在郁金香花型香槟酒杯的基础上，提升了杯体的高度，下部的设计则变得窄小，便于用户握持，整体造型简洁、优雅。设计师在杯体的外部做了一圈水平的标记，这是为了提醒用户，倒入的香槟达到这条水平线时，饮酒时的口感最佳。一套  6 只装，定价 47.5 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.madeindesign.com/prod-flute-a-champagne-richard-juhlin-optimum-29-cl-set-de-6-italesse-ref3056-clear.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233304yKU1klQz9FRE0mJ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233304Mo4x2kBhQUVS8cJK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233305majePW7xhI4DVHt9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233305EumaNspi3fOL6w7I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}